# Ghost Security MCP Server Configuration

# Required: Your Ghost Security API key
# Get this from your Ghost Security platform settings
GHOST_SECURITY_API_KEY=your-api-key-here

# Optional: Custom API base URL (defaults to https://api.ghostsecurity.ai/v1)
# GHOST_SECURITY_BASE_URL=https://api.ghostsecurity.ai/v1

# Optional: Scope all operations to a specific repository
# When set, findings operations will automatically filter to this repository
# GHOST_SECURITY_REPO_ID=your-repository-id

# Usage:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace 'your-api-key-here' with your actual Ghost Security API key
# 3. Optionally configure repository scoping by uncommenting and setting GHOST_SECURITY_REPO_ID